Context("Numeric");
#given
$i = random(1,3,.1);	

#image scale
$imgScale =0.4;

#image aspect ratio
$width = $imgScale*750;
$height = $imgScale*532;

#computation 
$p1 = 12*$i;
$p2 = 36*$i;
$p3 = -48*$i;

#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.01);

##############################################################
#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

[@ image( "UBC-CIR-17-001.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

In the following network, were [`I=[$i]`] [`A`], calculate the power supplied or absorbed by all of the elements.

[`P_1=`] [_____]{"$p1"} [`W`]  
[`P_2=`] [_____]{"$p2"} [`W`]  
[`P_3=`] [_____]{"$p3"} [`W`]  

END_PGML

